{
  "stem": "5430.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we wound up-- I remember going with the-- with the truck up to the river.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, they arranged to smuggle across by boat, by a little boat, a row boat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember I was scared, because I never knew how to swim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And water is not my favorite sport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- I was in the bottom of the-- of the boat when everyone is rowing quietly during the night, just pedaling across quietly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when we got to the other side, my brother told everybody-- I guess that was the pre-arranged-- that if we meet up with the Russian border patrol to tell them that we are on the way to Germany.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he said they would prevent us from going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so it happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We did wind up meeting up a Russian patrol.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we all kept saying, we're going to Germany, we're Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said, can't go it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Go back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Go back, sending us back in to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that, of course, was the whole plan to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they had-- they knew that that was the prearranged agreement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we wound up on the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we went to Krzemieniec or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I met my brother, George, who already arranged to have an apartment for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was a good looking guy, my brother, George.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And a lot of women were after him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they would do anything just to make a [INAUDIBLE] for him to marry their daughters and whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--he managed to get us this beautiful apartment up on a hill in the-- in the town of Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the meantime, my brother-- and he didn't go back yet.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
